g Dần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD-B%E1%BA%A1ch-y-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-b%E1%BA%B1ng-chu-lan-l%E1%BA%ADp/poem-n5TAomKSVJ6pQ-mCNkZFkA">Thái tang tử (Bạch y thường bằng chu lan lập) - 採桑子（白衣裳憑朱欗立）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-4UIcOQq3X5B-YNUldGF_5g">Nạp Lan Tính Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Tr%C3%A0-giang-thu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-ca/poem-43N05C4Futansq7ZKSooaA">Trà giang thu nguyệt ca - 茶江秋月歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C3%B9ng-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ph%C3%BA-b%E1%BA%A1ch-c%C3%BAc/poem-MeqYUB_JEXeRYS73_xGImQ">Trùng dương tịch thượng phú bạch cúc - 重陽蓆上賦白菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Trung-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Quan-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-AEC6I0cqYu-k5cNGd4tJCw">Trung thu dạ Đại Quan viên tức cảnh - 中秋夜大觀園即景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/V%C4%83n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%83-qu%C3%A1n/poem-CgDecTIWVtGC0EAtxc5orw">Văn Dương sứ để quán - 聞洋使抵館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-YRtbQ4Y_EBSiaNimbo26Cg">Lê Khắc Cẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
